---
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Career Wrapped | ClearCareer"
  description="Terms of service for ClearCareer Career Wrapped tools."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/wrapped" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-blue hover:text-blue-dark transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width={2}>
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Wrapped Tools
      </a>

      <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,2.5rem)] leading-[1.1] text-navy mb-8">
        Terms of Service for Career Wrapped Tools
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>
          By using ClearCareer's Career Wrapped tools, you agree to the following terms.
        </p>

        <h2>What These Tools Are</h2>
        <p>
          Career Wrapped tools (Career DNA, Roast My Resume, What You're Actually Worth, and Your Career in 5 Cards) are free, AI-powered tools that generate personalized career insights based on your resume. They are designed for entertainment and informational purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>AI-Generated Content</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Results are estimates, not facts.</strong> All salary figures, market value estimates, and career assessments are AI-generated approximations. They are not sourced from real-time salary databases or verified employer data.</li>
          <li><strong>Not financial or career advice.</strong> The results should not be used as the sole basis for salary negotiations, career decisions, or financial planning. They are starting points for your own research.</li>
          <li><strong>Source links are informational.</strong> When we link to salary research sites (Glassdoor, Payscale, Indeed, etc.), we generate URLs based on your title and location. The data on those sites may differ from our AI estimates. Always verify with the source directly.</li>
          <li><strong>AI can be wrong.</strong> The AI may misinterpret your resume, produce inaccurate salary estimates, or generate content that doesn't reflect your actual skills or experience. Use your own judgment.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Resume Roast Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          The "Roast My Resume" tool generates humorous, satirical commentary about your resume. The roasts are meant to be funny, not hurtful. If any generated content feels offensive or inappropriate, please contact us and we'll address it. The roasts reflect AI-generated comedy, not ClearCareer's assessment of your professional value.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Content</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>By uploading your resume, you confirm that you have the right to share its content and that it does not contain information belonging to someone else without their consent.</li>
          <li>You retain all rights to your resume. We do not claim any ownership of your uploaded content.</li>
          <li>As described in our <a href="/wrapped/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, your resume is not stored after analysis.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Shareable Links</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>When you generate results, you receive a shareable link. Anyone with this link can view your results.</li>
          <li>You are responsible for deciding who to share your link with. ClearCareer is not responsible for unintended distribution of your results.</li>
          <li>Shared results do not contain your resume text, only the generated insights.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Usage Limits</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Each tool is limited to one analysis per email address per 24 hours.</li>
          <li>We reserve the right to limit, suspend, or modify access to prevent abuse or manage costs.</li>
          <li>Automated or bulk use of these tools (via bots, scripts, or scrapers) is prohibited.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          ClearCareer provides these tools "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied. We are not liable for any decisions made based on the results, including but not limited to salary negotiations, job applications, or career changes. Your use of these tools is at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these terms at any time. The "last updated" date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions? Contact:<br />
          Izzy Piyale-Sheard<br />
          ClearCareer<br />
          <a href="mailto:izzy@joinclearcareer.com">izzy@joinclearcareer.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
